(266, 1, '2014-01-13 15:17:22', '2014-01-13 15:17:22', '<div style="font-size: 13px;">\r\n	<span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Tracey has always held a passion for Makeup Artistry since she was a little girl. She learnt about artistry in the form of Princesses and Princes though her fairy tale stories before bed time, fantasized about those pretty faces during daytime. Her biggest dream was to be able to bring them to life.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 13px;">\r\n	Now, a couple of decades later, her dream became true in 2008 when she became a professional Makeup Artist and Hair Stylist after graduating from The Makeup School in Auckland, New Zealand. She then went on doing freelance, experiencing in all avenues from Weddings, Film, Editorial to School Ball, Special Functions&hellip;anything you would call for a professional Hair and Makeup Artist.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 13px;">\r\n	Her professional experiences including&nbsp;<em>TVNZ show&nbsp;<span style="color: red;">Stars in Their Eyes, Shortland Street, Thin Lizzy</span>&nbsp;New Products Launching 2008,&nbsp;<span style="color: red;">Running with Scissors</span>&nbsp;Launching Ads,<span style="color: red;">Westfield Spring Fashion Show</span>, Sydney based&nbsp;<span style="color: red;">Cigs in Suit</span>&nbsp;New Product Launching 2012, various short films</em>&hellip; and the list go on.&nbsp;<strong>But she found her real passion in working with real women who might need a little something to accentuate the beauty they already possess. With a fresh perspective and a new splash of colour, Tracey loves to help put extra sparkle in a woman&rsquo;s smile and a new bounce in their step.</strong>Beyond her superb makeup and hair skills, her specialties&nbsp;and attributes that set her above the rest are&nbsp;in her people skills, her down to earth friendly manner and her ability to be able to make woman of all ages and stages feel comfortable, beautiful and confident. She has a unique skill set and absolutely loves what she does.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 13px;">\r\n	You have no reason to worry in the hand of Tracey for your special occasion or on your wedding day. She will ensure you leave feeling and looking fabulous.\r\n</p>\r\n', 'Tracey – Lead Makeup Artist and Owner of Beautiful You Makeup & Hair.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tracey', '', '', '2014-01-13 15:25:48', '2014-01-13 15:25:48', '', 0, 'http://wordpress.local/?page_id=266', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(267, 1, '2014-01-13 15:15:23', '2014-01-13 15:15:23', '<div>\n	<strong>2.1. Tracey &ndash; Lead Makeup Artist and Owner of Beautiful You Makeup &amp; Hair.</strong>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n	&nbsp;\n</div>\n\n<p>\n	Tracey has always held a passion for Makeup Artistry since she was a little girl. She learnt about artistry in the form of Princesses and Princes though her fairy tale stories before bed time, fantasized about those pretty faces during daytime. Her biggest dream was to be able to bring them to life.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	Now, a couple of decades later, her dream became true in 2008 when she became a professional Makeup Artist and Hair Stylist after graduating from The Makeup School in Auckland, New Zealand. She then went on doing freelance, experiencing in all avenues from Weddings, Film, Editorial to School Ball, Special Functions&hellip;anything you would call for a professional Hair and Makeup Artist.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	Her professional experiences including <em>TVNZ show <span style="color:red">Stars in Their Eyes, Shortland Street, Thin Lizzy</span> New Products Launching 2008, <span style="color:red">Running with Scissors</span> Launching Ads,<span style="color:red">Westfield Spring Fashion Show</span>, Sydney based <span style="color:red">Cigs in Suit</span> New Product Launching 2012, various short films</em>&hellip; and the list go on. <strong>But she found her real passion in working with real women who might need a little something to accentuate the beauty they already possess. With a fresh perspective and a new splash of colour, Tracey loves to help put extra sparkle in a woman&rsquo;s smile and a new bounce in their step.</strong>Beyond her superb makeup and hair skills, her specialties&nbsp;and attributes that set her above the rest are&nbsp;in her people skills, her down to earth friendly manner and her ability to be able to make woman of all ages and stages feel comfortable, beautiful and confident. She has a unique skill set and absolutely loves what she does.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	You have no reason to worry in the hand of Tracey for your special occasion or on your wedding day. She will ensure you leave feeling and looking fabulous.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	<strong>2.2 Monique</strong>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	<a href="http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/monique1.png"><img alt="monique" src="http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/monique1.png" /></a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	Monique had experience in and out of salons for 7 years doing work in formal hair, weddings and photoshoots. Along with all our artists, her style is consistent with the unique BYMH style: defined, timeless art of &ldquo;hairdressing&rdquo;.&nbsp; She is competent in doing classic or more contemporary styles using hot irons, rollers, pins, hair peices and braiding, creating and delivers effective beautiful result.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	A love note from Monique:\n</p>\n\n<p>\n	<em>&ldquo;It is my aim in hairdressing to make the person feel comfortable and confident in the style and to compromise their ideas with my experience and suggestions&rdquo;</em>\n</p>\n', 'The Experts', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '77-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-01-13 15:15:23', '2014-01-13 15:15:23', '', 77, 'http://wordpress.local/77-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
