(280, 1, '2014-01-13 15:29:13', '2014-01-13 15:29:13', '<p style="font-size: 13px;">\n	<span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Monique had experience in and out of salons for 7 years doing work in formal hair, weddings and photoshoots. Along with all our artists, her style is consistent with the unique BYMH style: defined, timeless art of &ldquo;hairdressing&rdquo;.&nbsp; She is competent in doing classic or more contemporary styles using hot irons, rollers, pins, hair peices and braiding, creating and delivers effective beautiful result.</span>\n</p>\n\n<p style="font-size: 13px;">\n	A love note from Monique:\n</p>\n\n<p style="font-size: 13px;">\n	<em>&ldquo;It is my aim in hairdressing to make the person feel comfortable and confident in the style and to compromise their ideas with my experience and suggestions&rdquo;</em>\n</p>\n\n<div class="photo_right">\n	<p style="font-size: 13px;">\n		<a href="http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/monique1.png"><img alt="monique" src="http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/monique1.png" /></a>\n	</p>\n</div>\n', 'Monique', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '269-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-01-13 15:29:13', '2014-01-13 15:29:13', '', 269, 'http://wordpress.local/269-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(281, 1, '2014-01-13 15:33:12', '2014-01-13 15:33:12', '<p>\r\n	Test pages\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<a href="http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/blog_detail_img01.jpg"><img alt="blog_detail_img01" class="size-medium wp-image-118 aligncenter" height="300" src="http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/blog_detail_img01-300x300.jpg" width="300" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	Our partnership with Sony continues with a new launch for PIIQ - Sony&#39;s slick, new brand of headphones. The site features a multitude of finely tuned interactive details including rollover animations, subtle movements and navigational elements.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	The full product lineup gives visitors huge, sexy product images, sharing tools, sweet product pairings, and the ability to add comments with Facebook integration. The PIIQ Team pages offer up inside details of new members, their gear and stats and the news section keeps fans up-to-date on all things PIIQ.<br />\r\n	There&#39;s quite a bit of cool stuff to check out so take a look at the new Sony PIIQ and let us know what you think.\r\n</p>\r\n', 'Test', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-13 15:33:12', '2014-01-13 15:33:12', '', 61, 'http://wordpress.local/61-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
